  "title": "Electrical Engineer / Assistant Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Job Description</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Installation, commissioning, maintenance and testing of equipment.</li>\n  <li>Compile field service reports after servicing of equipment.</li>\n  <li>Provides product, service, or equipment technical and engineering information by answering questions and requests.</li>\n  <li>Maintains product database, entering data.</li>\n  <li>Maintains professional and technical knowledge.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Job Requirements</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Electrical &amp; Electronic Engineering or higher</li>\n  <li>Strong interpersonal skill</li>\n  <li>Good analyzing information and verbal communication skills</li>\n  <li>Class 3 driving license</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Additional Notes:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Opportunities for overseas training and job.</li>\n  <li>On the job training and Safety training will be provided.</li>\n</ul>",
